name: Organized
description:
This is one of my favorite paintings in the collection right now. The color really brightens up a room, it just cheers me up.

Size | 24"w x 24"h and the canvas is stretched on a 1.25" thick canvas. A frame is not necessary, it can hang directly on the wall.

Medium | Professional grade acrylic on canvas

Style | Modern, Contemporary, Urban, Abstract


Note: Your art will be shipped to you and packed with protective packaging, whenever possible I try to use recycled or green packing material.

Thanks for your interest in my work, feel free to contact me with any questions.

name: Round Leaf Plant
description:
I found this plant on my street with round leaves. I clipped a branch to take home because I thought it was so interesting. This canvas was painted while holding the branch of this weird plant in my hand.
